Title: The Mafia Is No Longer What It Used to Be
Writer: Uliano Greca, Francesco Guttuso, Giuliano La Franca, Franco Maresco, Claudia Uzzo
Actors: Letizia Battaglia, Ciccio Mira, Federica Scibilia
Plot: On the 25th anniversary of Capaci and via D'Amelio bombings, Franco Maresco wonders what's left of their ideals and struggles in contemporary Sicily, dwelling on its relationship with the Mafia.
